data.title: Dreams of Dark and Light: The Great Short Fiction of Tanith Lee
data.meta_description: Dreams of Dark and Light: The Great Short Fiction of Tanith Lee is a collection of fantasy, horror and science fiction stories by author Tanith Lee. It was released in 1986 and was the author's first book published by Arkham House. It was published in an edition of 3,957 copies.
